Setup
=====

Run:

    npm install -g grunt-cli
    npm install
    rbenv install
    bundle

Builds
======

Run:

    grunt

To test/iterate with a live-reload server:

    grunt server

Releases
========

On new release:

- make cdnjs pull request
- update change log
- update front page download links, version, size, date
- update cdnjs link in quickstart, tutorial, jsfiddles
- update infelicities (if any fixed) and other documentation
- update dependencies (if any change) in the jsfiddles
